107
00:06:55,482 --> 00:06:56,677
Oh, shut up, Cullum.

108
00:06:57,350 --> 00:06:59,342
I'll get you in soon, okay?

109
00:07:01,688 --> 00:07:04,351
Pratt, knee contusions, slipped
at work, can't bear weight.

110
00:07:04,524 --> 00:07:06,823
I've got a hot MI so
it's gonna have to wait.

111
00:07:06,993 --> 00:07:10,293
I didn't say it can't wait. I said
"can't bear weight," as in stand up.

112
00:07:10,463 --> 00:07:12,625
I'll get to it when I get to it.

113
00:07:12,799 --> 00:07:16,634
Plan to help Residents communicate,
you might wanna start with Pratt.

114
00:07:16,803 --> 00:07:19,238
Tell me the truth. How
many Vicodin will it take...

115
00:07:19,406 --> 00:07:21,534
for you to go away?
I'll write it down.

116
00:07:22,008 --> 00:07:23,738
I'm doomed. Morris!

117
00:07:24,377 --> 00:07:26,369
Relax and come talk
to me when you're done.

118
00:07:26,913 --> 00:07:28,814
- Hi.
- Hi.

119
00:07:28,982 --> 00:07:30,314
- Going home?
- Yeah.

120
00:07:30,483 --> 00:07:34,045
