460
00:25:10,576 --> 00:25:12,306
- So how are you doing?
- Good.

461
00:25:12,511 --> 00:25:14,912
- Really?
- Mm-hm. Never better.

462
00:25:15,414 --> 00:25:18,646
- Really?
- Yes, yes, yes.

463
00:25:19,018 --> 00:25:22,921
I processed feelings of anger, shame and
guilt in an emotionally safe environment.

